description:
Our pal Elijah is the star of this week's War Chest Update. We shot this solo scene with him a while back, before he became a regular in many of our features.

You can find Elijah in such Active Duty videos as Below Deck 2, Long Deployment 2, Active Duty Live Vol. 2, About Face, Soldier's Ball 3: Bareback Waltz, Troop Review, Long Deployment, Fire in the Hole 2 and his debut in Rear Gunners 3. Dang, Elijah's been a busy little bee, hasn't he?

Elijah has also starred in the Dirty Bird Pictures features Grindass House and Army Strongarm.
title: Elijah
